name: Butterfly Photogram
description: This a hand made photogram of a stencil of butterflies, it measures 10"x8" and is incredibly detailed. Due to the process of making this product each print is unique and different from each other. They come in either black butterflies with a white background and vice versa. They will be numbered and signed. They are incredibly charming simple pieces to have blu-tacked to the wall or framed!

name: Old School Robot Skateboard
description:
This skateboard is one from a project I have created, I take in peoples old and unused skateboard decks which are just gathering dust in the garage sand them down and design them so that they have a new life as art. This board is an old school skateboard deck and features a silver chrome finish.

This deck is the first robot in the series and uses spray paint and acrylic.

PLEASE NOTE that these are used skateboards so there will be imperfections in the woodwork due to use.

Will be sent with signed card and packaged nicely to ensure its safe arrival.
